text: Shuangxi District () is a rural district in the eastern part of New Taipei City, Taiwan. ==Tourist attractions== Map including Shuangxi (labeled as Shuang-ch’i (Sōkei) ) (1950) * Beishi River Historical Trail * Pingxi Historical Trail * Buyan Pavilion * Shuangxi Sanzhong Temple ==Transportation== * TRA Mudan Station * TRA Shuangxi Station ==See also== * New Taipei City ==References== ==External links== * Shuangxi District Office, New Taipei City Category:Districts of New Taipei
